definition.value: An androstanoid that is 5alpha-androstane having a hydroxy substituent at the 3alpha-position and an oxo group at the 17-position. It is a metabolite of dehydroepiandrosterone .
A guanidinoacetate having a phospho group attached to the primary amino part of the guanidine moiety.
A hydroxyisoflavanone that is 2,3-dihydrodaidzein with an additonal hydroxy substituent at position 2'.
